<div id="review_3938899219" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3938899219" />
    <a title="Slobodan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/133251207-slobodan"><img alt="Slobodan" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1618126450p2/133251207.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3938899219?book_show_action=true">Jul 20, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Slobodan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Slobodan" href="/user/show/133251207-slobodan">Slobodan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback 9782253115571" href="/book/show/1838025.Trait_d_ath_ologie">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3938899219" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1981444284974546837">In this book Onfray demystifies three major religions of our Western, Europe/Middle East civilizations: Christianity, Judaism and Islam. He deconstructs their myths, exposes their hypocrisy, double standards and means to keep their followers obedient. And he does that in a precise, argument, scientific way yet using witty, everyday language. A great book, in my opinion.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


